Reasoning: 
- cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on agent-based models and their optimisation. 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is also likely as ABMs are commonly used to model social systems. 
- cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) is relevant as the paper applies ABMs to a transportation system. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper discusses data assimilation techniques to improve model accuracy. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is also relevant as the paper discusses the use of ABMs in an Intelligent Transport System.
